  "prompt": "Which is a suitable solar panel installation provider in La Habra, California CA?",
  "response": "When looking for a suitable solar panel installation provider in La Habra, California, it's important to consider companies with a good reputation, experience, and customer reviews. Here are a few solar providers you can explore:\n\n1. **Sunrun** - Known for residential solar solutions, Sunrun has a variety of financing options to suit different needs.\n\n2. **Vivint Solar** - They offer customized solar solutions and are known for their customer service.\n\n3. **Sungevity** - They provide a range of solar services and are recognized for their online tools that make the process easy.\n\n4. **Palmetto Solar** - Offers solar panel installation and has a focus on eco-friendly practices, along with good financing options.\n\n5. **Tesla Energy** - Provides solar panel installation along with its solar roof products, known for innovative technology.\n\n6. **EnergySage** - While not a provider, this platform allows you to compare quotes from different local installers to find the best option for your needs.\n\nIt\u2019s advisable to get multiple quotes, read customer reviews, and check for licenses and warranties before making a decision. Additionally, local contractors may also provide competitive pricing and personalized service.",
